NK089(hu)001:9423: de dag ni zhar las byung ba'am zhal las byung ba'i log pa gsum du'ang bka' stsal to //
NK089(hu)001:9424: mi shes 'di gnyis bzhir snang ba //
NK089(hu)001:9425: dman rigs dang ni rigs ma nges //
NK089(hu)001:9426: rigs chad 'du shes can 'di dag /kun nas dkrigs pa'i mun pa yin //
NK089(hu)001:9427: zhes pa ma rtogs pa phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen la'ang gnyis gnyis bzhir gyes pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:9428: phyal ba la'ang dman pa'i shes pa ma rig pas mgo rmongs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9429: log lta gang du'ang rigs ma nges pas rkyen la rag lus pa can gnyis so //
NK089(hu)001:9431: rigs chad pas byang chub kyi myu gu rtsa ba 'tshig pa ba dang 'du shes can no //
NK089(hu)001:9432: de ni yang dag pa'i don mthong du mi ster
NK089(hu)001:9433: bas sngar bshad pa'i sgo kun nas dkrigs pa'i mun
NK089(hu)001:9434: par gyur pa nyid du bstan to //
NK089(hu)001:9435: 'du shes can bzhi chags pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:9436: gang la g.yeng dang ya nga can //
NK089(hu)001:9437: mos pa can zhes grags pa rnams //
NK089(hu)001:9438: zhes pa rgyang 'phen gnyis pa 'du shes can la'ang dbye na bzhi ste /
NK089(hu)001:9439: tshe 'di'i 'tsho ba longs spyod mthu la'ang tsho la sogs 'dod chen po dang /
NK089(hu)001:9440: bya ba dang nyo tshong dang longs spyod kyi phyir
NK089(hu)001:9441: mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba 'jig rten gyi gtsug lag lta
NK089(hu)001:9443: tshe bdag dang 'khor gyi phyir rgyu 'bras la rten
NK089(hu)001:9444: pa med par 'di'i khyad par gyi ched du sdig
NK089(hu)001:9445: spyod pa dang / rang gi lta phyin ci log
NK089(hu)001:9446: tu gyur kyang bas sangs rgyas pa la shin tu
NK089(hu)001:9447: mos pa can zhes bka' rgyud las grags pa bzhin
NK089(hu)001:9448: spyod pa dang / ni / gtan nas rigs chad pa ma yin te /
NK089(hu)001:9449: bde bar gshegs pa'i rgyu can rkyen dang 'phrad na grol thar gyi rten yod pas /
NK089(hu)001:9450: rgyal ba'i zhing khams mi mjed 'dir 'byung ste /
NK089(hu)001:9451: brgyud nas lan gcig thar pa'ang 'thob bo //
NK089(hu)001:9452: 'di dag ni rigs chad dang rgyang 'phen nyid dang
NK089(hu)001:9453: drug ni bshad pa'i log zhen sde drug brgyud pa'o
NK089(hu)001:9455: rang bzhin log pa rnams bstan pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:9456: log par rtog 'di ya mtshan can //
NK089(hu)001:9457: brgya phrag gsum dang drug cu gnyis //
NK089(hu)001:9458: nyi shu'am sde bcu lnga gnyis la //
NK089(hu)001:9459: tha dad rnam pa du mar snang //
NK089(hu)001:9460: zhes pa mur rtug dang mu stegs kyi lta ba rang bzhin gyis log pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:9461: 'di la'ang nang ris mang po gyes pas ngo mtshar gyi mngon shes can yang yod de /
NK089(hu)001:9464: lta ba drug cu rtsa gnyis ni sngon gyi mtha' la rtog pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK089(hu)001:9465: phyi ma'i mtha' la rtog pa bco brgyad de drug cu ni /
NK089(hu)001:9466: sngon mu stegs kyis mngon shes skyes pa'i lo rgyus kyis bstan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9467: gzhi ma rtag chad gnyis te drug cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK089(hu)001:9468: log pa'i ri bo nyi shu ni /
NK089(hu)001:9469: phung po lnga yi gzugs gcig pu la'ang gzugs bdag yin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9472: bdag dang ldan pa bzhir rtogs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9473: de bzhin bzhi phrag lnga la nyi shu'o //
NK089(hu)001:9474: de ltar dus gsum gyi phung po la rtogs pas drug cur yang 'gyur ro //
NK089(hu)001:9475: ston pa drug gi lta ba'i sde mi mthun pa
NK089(hu)001:9476: phra men spyod lung la rten sogs bcu'o bcu gsungs
NK089(hu)001:9477: pa dang / log lta 'jig tshogs mthar 'dzin la sogs pa lnga dang /
NK089(hu)001:9478: gzhi tha dad rtag chad gnyis la sogs pa rnam
NK089(hu)001:9479: pa du mar mi mthun par snang ba rnams so
NK089(hu)001:9480: // yod dang med pa'i phyogs 'dzin las //
NK089(hu)001:9481: zhes pa sde gnyis ni rtsa ba 'a di nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:9482: chad pa 'bring has pa'i lugs tshe 'dir glo bur du skyes la mtha' chad par bsgrub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9483: rtag par lta ba'i snying gi dkyil na yod pa'i
NK089(hu)001:9484: ngo bo de gtan tshigs lnga dang bzhis bsgrub pa
NK089(hu)001:9485: dang / las 'byung khungs kyi don gyis gzhi lta
NK089(hu)001:9486: ba thams cad kyi rtsa ba'o de las sngar gyes
NK089(hu)001:9487: dang / pa'i phyir / 'jig pa'i tshogs dang mthar 'dzin dang //
NK089(hu)001:9488: log par 'dzin dang lta khyad can //
NK089(hu)001:9489: rang gi brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin te //
NK089(hu)001:9490: ris mi mthun pa sde lngar grags //
NK089(hu)001:9491: rang bzhin log pa log pa nyid //
NK089(hu)001:9492: ces pa log lta sde lnga gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:9493: bshad pa'i brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin lnga sde pa'o zhes pa 'dir yang mjal te /
NK089(hu)001:9494: gang gis gang 'jig pa ni 'jig pa ste 'jig
NK089(hu)001:9495: pa'i rgyu yod pas 'jig pas zhig pa ni grub
NK089(hu)001:9496: mtha' zer ro // phung po lnga'i 'jig tshogs la lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9497: rtag chad gangs ka la 'dzin pa ste gang mur
NK089(hu)001:9498: bzungs zhe mtha' yin kyang ma rtogs pas mthar 'dzin
NK089(hu)001:9499: pa'o // mthar 'dzin par lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9500: yang dag pa ma yin pa la der bzung ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:9502: lta ba log la zhes pas yang dag pa la
NK089(hu)001:9503: sun bton te nga rgyal bzung ba'o mchog tu 'dzin
NK089(hu)001:9504: pa dang / tshul khrims khyi phag me lnga bsten
NK089(hu)001:9505: dbyug gu gsum sogs dang brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin
NK089(hu)001:9506: pa dang / pa dang / lta ba ris mi
NK089(hu)001:9507: mthun pa lnga po 'di ni rkyen gyis ma bsgyur
NK089(hu)001:9508: bar thog ma nyid nas rang bzhin gyis log sde
NK089(hu)001:9509: pa dang / pa dang / pa ste / dmus
NK089(hu)001:9510: long lta bu 'di la lta ba'i rtsa ba sde
NK089(hu)001:9511: pa dang / pa dang / pa ste / drug go // gzhan rkyen log pa phra men spyod //
NK089(hu)001:9512: lus la brten dang rtags tsam 'dzin //
NK089(hu)001:9513: zhes pa zhar byung rkyen gzhan gyis bslad nas log ltar gyur ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:9514: lta ba yang 'dres dge sdig gi las 'dres mar spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9515: phyin ci ma log pa'i lung gi shes rab dang
NK089(hu)001:9516: man ngag gis ma zin pa'i phyogs tsam la brten
NK089(hu)001:9517: pa dang / rten skyabs log pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9518: sangs rgyas pa'i rtags tsam chos gos sogs 'dzin pa
NK089(hu)001:9519: gzhan yang gsang ba'i tshig dang gsang rdzas 'chang dang
NK089(hu)001:9520: bzhi'o // de la yang spyir yan lag drug ste /
NK089(hu)001:9521: bcos mar spyod dang mu cor smra //
NK089(hu)001:9522: lung gi phyogs tsam rten pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:9523: phyogs log gol dang bslab pa 'chal //
NK089(hu)001:9524: phyogs ltos gcod pa rnam bzhir grags //
NK089(hu)001:9525: zhes pa rnam grangs gnyis nyid de dngos rnam pa drug sgra bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:9527: gnyis pa la gcig /gsum pa la gnyis /
NK089(hu)001:9529: bcos ma gzhan pas gyur pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:9530: 'di las gyur pa gnyis kho na //
NK089(hu)001:9531: zhes pa phyogs phyi ma rgyas pa'i yan lag tu 'grel ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:9532: dang po mu stegs bcos mar spyod pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK089(hu)001:9533: gzhan bdag gi ba las gyur pa dang bdag nyid las gyur pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9534: gnas dang 'khor dang yo byad nor //
NK089(hu)001:9535: longs spyod lngar ldan gzhan las gyur //
NK089(hu)001:9536: zhes pa nyid kyi yan lag gzhan las gyur pa'i lta ngan ni /
NK089(hu)001:9537: gnas la bdag gir 'dzin par gyur pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9539: yo byad la bdag gir 'dzin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9540: nor la bdag gir 'dzin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9541: longs spyod la bdag gir 'dzin pa dang lnga'i lta ba can te /
NK089(hu)001:9542: dngos po de nyid kyis rtsa ba'i ming nges par 'grub bo //
NK089(hu)001:9543: dran pa rtag lta ltos 'dzin rgyu //
NK089(hu)001:9544: med pa'i mtha' dang mtha' med shes //
NK089(hu)001:9545: kun nas rnam par mi g.yeng lta //
NK089(hu)001:9546: zhes pa 'di las gyur ba'ang bdag gi snga ma
NK089(hu)001:9547: la ci byas dran pa'i sems rtag par lta ba
NK089(hu)001:9548: dang / de ltos shing bdag gir 'dzin te de la kun 'byung rdul dang /
NK089(hu)001:9550: snying stobs dag la bdag gir 'gyur pas rang bzhin rgyur lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9551: rgyur lta ba de'ang dran rtag chos thams cad dang
NK089(hu)001:9552: 'bras bu med par shes pa'o min par med pa'i
NK089(hu)001:9553: mtha' dang 'dod pa'ang shes shing lan gcig na mtha'
NK089(hu)001:9555: stong pa 'ba' zhig tu lta ba'ang mtha' med pa shes pas /
NK089(hu)001:9556: bdag tu lta ba la brten nas snang la don
NK089(hu)001:9557: med par dbang po bsdams te rtse gcig pa'o mi
NK089(hu)001:9558: rtog pa kun nas rnam par mi g.yeng blta la
NK089(hu)001:9559: sogs pa bsgom pa mu stegs kyi bsam gtan la
NK089(hu)001:9560: gnas pa snyoms par 'jug pa bdun sde pa lta
NK089(hu)001:9561: bu'o // gang du shes pa yod smra lta //
NK089(hu)001:9562: de bzhin med par lta ba dang //
NK089(hu)001:9564: gang du yod min med min lta //
NK089(hu)001:9566: zhes pa mu cor smra ba'ang mi bden pa'i gzhung smra bas ming nges par 'grub ste /
NK089(hu)001:9567: de la rnam par shes brtag pa rdzas su yod
NK089(hu)001:9568: par lta ba rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched lta
NK089(hu)001:9569: bu ste / nga ni rtag la blo ni 'gyur //
NK089(hu)001:9571: phung po nying mtshams sbyor ba dang //
NK089(hu)001:9572: rdza bcag byi 'phur ji bzhin du //
NK089(hu)001:9573: rtag pa the bong yungs 'bru tsam //
NK089(hu)001:9574: bdag ces bya ba des len to //
NK089(hu)001:9576: de bzhin med par lta ba'ang rnam shes la rdzas su med par 'dod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9577: da ltar gyi tshe 'dir bzang ngan kun brtag pa'i ngo bo de las 'byung bar lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9578: tshe dngos po 'di gang 'di dag yod par 'gyur
NK089(hu)001:9579: ram med par 'gyur lta ba'ang yod na rta ga
NK089(hu)001:9580: la med na chad pa'i phyir 'du shes ni yod
NK089(hu)001:9581: pa'ang ma yin med pa'ang ma yin par lta ba
NK089(hu)001:9582: yod phung po gsum pa lta bu min med min
NK089(hu)001:9583: gyi skye mched lta bu la sogs brgyad du lta
NK089(hu)001:9584: ba dang / da ltar gyi tshe 'di yod la
NK089(hu)001:9585: phyi ma phan chad med par lta bas spyod yul
NK089(hu)001:9586: kun kyang mya ngan las 'das par 'dod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9587: bshad pa las ni mu cor smra ba sde bzhi po zhes gsungs pas /
NK089(hu)001:9588: 'dir de don brtag par gces so //
NK089(hu)001:9589: gang 'dir phyogs tsam brten pa ni //
NK089(hu)001:9590: gang ma yin pa ma yin nyid //
NK089(hu)001:9592: rgyal ba'i lung gi gang 'dir phyogs tsam la brten pa ni gcig ste /
NK089(hu)001:9593: gang yod pa'ang ma yin med pa'ang ma yin pa
NK089(hu)001:9594: ci'ang ma yin pa nyid kyang ma yin pa zhig
NK089(hu)001:9595: par 'dod pa'o // phyogs log log par gang 'gyur pa //
NK089(hu)001:9596: drug ste so so tha dad dang //
NK089(hu)001:9597: spyir lta gang rig skyon med pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9598: rgyur lta spyod pas dag par lta //
NK089(hu)001:9599: 'tsho ba bcos pas dag lta dang //
NK089(hu)001:9600: rgyun la lhwam dang gos bcos pa //
NK089(hu)001:9601: skra spu bcos dang rgyan can dang //
NK089(hu)001:9602: dka' thub bsten pas drag po'o //
NK089(hu)001:9604: lta ba'i phyogs ril log pas log pa'i dbang du song ba'i nges tshigs 'grub ste /
NK089(hu)001:9605: de'i 'dod gzhung yang 'chad pa'i lta ba'i sde drug pos bye brag dang /
NK089(hu)001:9606: spyi'i mu stegs kyi lta ba gang ltar shes kyang skyon med de /
NK089(hu)001:9607: des thar pa thob par lta ba gnyis so //
NK089(hu)001:9608: de la khas blangs pa'i sde drug dngos ni /
NK089(hu)001:9609: rgyur lta ba'i sde la'ang byed pa po rgyur lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9611: ngo bo nyid rgyur lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9612: rang bzhin rgyur lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9613: rdul phra rab rgyur lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:9614: dbang phyug rgyur lta ba las /
NK089(hu)001:9615: 'dir byed pa po rgyur lta ba dang po'o //
NK089(hu)001:9616: spyod pa khrus dang gtsang sbra 'ba' tshig spyad pas rtag pa dag par lta ba gnyis /
NK089(hu)001:9617: bza' btung bcos te gtsang ma zas gcig pa'am sha
NK089(hu)001:9618: stag zos pas thar par lta ba dang gsum mo
NK089(hu)001:9619: // spyod pa dus thams cad du cha lugs bcos
NK089(hu)001:9620: nas spyod pa thob par lta ba'ang lhwam gos kha
NK089(hu)001:9621: dog dbyibs rgyan bsgyur ba dang bzhi /
NK089(hu)001:9622: skra dang kha spu bregs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9623: ral par byas nas gnas pa ste mdor gcer bu pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9624: ma pham skra'i lwa ba can lta bu'o //
NK089(hu)001:9625: lus la rus pa thod pa dang thal bas brgyan pa'i rgyan can pa dang lnga /
NK089(hu)001:9626: bya dang khyi dang me lnga bsten pa la nyi
NK089(hu)001:9627: zla bzung dang chu mi btung ba sogs pa'i dka'
NK089(hu)001:9628: thub drag por bsten pa dang drug go //
NK089(hu)001:9629: byed pa po rgyu ni lta gzhi ste gzhan drug go //
NK089(hu)001:9631: brten pas dag lta rten rtog dang //
NK089(hu)001:9632: rten chags byin chags bkra shis mtshan //
NK089(hu)001:9634: zhes pa lta ngan gyi sel zhugs pas shes pa 'chal ba ni gsum ste /
NK089(hu)001:9635: dbang phyug rgyur lta ba 'jig rten 'di la phya'am dbang phyug chen po bsten cing /
NK089(hu)001:9636: des mtho ris ngan song du gtong bar 'a dod de /
NK089(hu)001:9637: gang zhig phra rgyu gcig pu skye gnas 'dug /de yis 'di kun skye shing 'jig par byed //
NK089(hu)001:9638: skye ba po 'di shes pa yod min te //
NK089(hu)001:9639: dbang phyug gis btang yang na g.yang sa'am //
NK089(hu)001:9640: mtho ris dag tu 'gro ba kho nar byed //
NK089(hu)001:9641: ces 'byung ba lta bur 'dod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9642: rdul phra rab rgyur smra ba pas /
NK089(hu)001:9643: dang por 'jig rten chags pa'i tshe rdul phra rab
NK089(hu)001:9644: kyi rdzas 'dus pa las lha tshangs pa'i sgo nga
NK089(hu)001:9645: shin tu 'od 'bar ba zhig byung nas de smin
NK089(hu)001:9646: pa las lha tshangs pa chen po gdong bzhi la
NK089(hu)001:9647: ral pa can zhig byung nas 'jig rten thams cad
NK089(hu)001:9648: byas te chags par 'dod pa brten chags dang /
NK089(hu)001:9649: chos mi dge ba lus ngag gi bdun bsrungs pas
NK089(hu)001:9650: lha'i byin chags shing bkra shis par 'dod pa dang
NK089(hu)001:9651: gsum ste / de dag ni 'khor ba'i 'jigs skyobs lob pa'i dbang du gyur pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9652: phyogs ltos gcod pa gang zhe na //
NK089(hu)001:9653: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhi pa 'chad de /
NK089(hu)001:9654: yang dag pa'i lam gyi phyogs su spyi yud tsam
NK089(hu)001:9655: la ltos nas bdag 'dzin dang ma bral ba'i phyir
NK089(hu)001:9656: de la bzhi ni sgra bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:9657: gang 'dir phyi rol rnam pa gsum //
NK089(hu)001:9658: bye brag pa dang tha snyad pa //
NK089(hu)001:9659: rang snang phyogs gcig gcod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9660: zhes pa mu stegs phyi rol pa la'ang rnam pa gsum ste /
NK089(hu)001:9661: rdul phra rab sil bu dus gsum rtag par 'dod pa dang mu stegs bye brag pa /
NK089(hu)001:9662: 'dus pa rang bzhin rtag par 'dod mdo sde pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9663: yul med pa'i shes pa rtag par 'dod mu stegs rang sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:9664: de dag gi lta ba dang gzhi mthun pa la bdag 'dzin dang ma bral ba'i cha mthun pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9665: yang dag phra dang zab pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:9666: rgya cher yangs pa de kho na //
NK089(hu)001:9667: zhes pa ltos nas btags pa'i mu stegs yang dag pa la gsum ste /
NK089(hu)001:9668: mu stegs rtsen min yang dag rnam bcas dang rnam
NK089(hu)001:9669: med kyi shes pa gnyis ka rtag pa smra ba'i
NK089(hu)001:9670: phra ba rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma pa dang
NK089(hu)001:9671: / glo bur la ci'ang ma yin pa gcig rtag
NK089(hu)001:9672: smra zab pa mu stegs rtsen min mdo sde spyod
NK089(hu)001:9674: ci'ang mi gnas yid la byas pa rgya che yangs
NK089(hu)001:9675: pa mu stegs ton min gzhung phyi ma'i dbu ma
NK089(hu)001:9676: pa ste / yang dag pa'i theg pa gsum dang
NK089(hu)001:9677: lta ba'i cha mthun pa de nyid bdag tu 'dzin
NK089(hu)001:9678: pa'i phyir gol bar sbyar to //
NK089(hu)001:9679: gsang sngags rigs byed rigs spyod dang //
NK089(hu)001:9680: rigs sbyor dam par phyogs ltos gcod //
NK089(hu)001:9681: ces pa cha mthun pa'i mu stegs gsang sngags pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK089(hu)001:9682: rigs gsum rtag rigs byed kri ya pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9683: lta spyod gnyis med 'dzin rigs spyod u pa ya dang /
NK089(hu)001:9684: sems rtag pas byin rlabs lhar snang ba'ang rtag rigs
NK089(hu)001:9685: sbyor yo ga ba spyod pa gtsor mi byed pas
NK089(hu)001:9686: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyogs 'ba' zhig gtsor spyod pa'o
NK089(hu)001:9687: // gsang chen brtul zhugs chen spyod dang //
NK089(hu)001:9688: rgyal dpog pa dang rgyal thabs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9689: zhes pa mu stegs gsang sngags pa las khyad par gyur pa gsang chen pa la gsum ste /
NK089(hu)001:9690: blang dor med par dam rdzas dang thabs shes la
NK089(hu)001:9691: 'dzin spyod pa brtul zhugs cher spyod pa ma h+aa
NK089(hu)001:9692: yo ga dang / rgyal po dbyings ye shes a
NK089(hu)001:9693: ti yo ga'i rjes su 'jug pa a nu yo
NK089(hu)001:9694: yo ga dang / ga ba dang / bya ba
NK089(hu)001:9695: bral ba'i ngo bo rang byung ye shes 'dzin thams
NK089(hu)001:9696: ca da kyi bdag po a ti yo ga pa'o
NK089(hu)001:9697: yo ga dang / ga ba dang / // 'di
NK089(hu)001:9698: dag lta ba'i gzhung ni bsgrub mi dgos te yang
NK089(hu)001:9699: dag pa'i lam gyi lta ba las bdag 'dzin can
NK089(hu)001:9701: yang dag pa'i lta ba dang skad tshul ji lta ba gcig kyang rtog 'dzin gyis phye ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:9702: mu stegs 'di dag ni dus deng sang gi lam
NK089(hu)001:9703: par khas 'ches pa dag la'ang shin tu'ang mang ngo
NK089(hu)001:9704: // de bas nan tur du bya zhing bshad pa'i
NK089(hu)001:9705: bla ma dag la thugs nas sgo kun bsdur bar
NK089(hu)001:9706: // rigs so // zhar las byung ba gang 'di dag /mtha' yas sder byung rdzogs pa sde //
NK089(hu)001:9707: gang mu zin pa de rtag 'dzin //
NK089(hu)001:9708: sangs rgyas kun gyi nye gnas so //
NK089(hu)001:9709: zhes pa yang dag pa'i bstan pa'i zhar las byung
NK089(hu)001:9710: ba'i mu stegs phra men pa yan chad rnam grangs
NK089(hu)001:9711: mang po mtha' yas bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig
NK089(hu)001:9712: spyir yod kyang / 'dir mu stegs gsang sngags pa
NK089(hu)001:9713: che chung drug man chad kun bshad pa'i rtsa ba
NK089(hu)001:9716: de lta bu gang rang rang gi lta ba'i mu
NK089(hu)001:9717: zin cing zhen pa dag ni don thog tu ma
NK089(hu)001:9718: phebs pas rtags la 'dzin pa tsam las /
NK089(hu)001:9719: rgyal ba sangs rgyas ring bar 'grub pa'i rgyu yod pas nye gnas te /
NK089(hu)001:9720: rtags tsam 'dzin pa dang zhar byung gnyis ngo bo gcig pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9721: 'o na 'dir bshad pa las zhar byung ni log
NK089(hu)001:9722: pa cha gnyis po las brtags pa 'dra'o zhe na
NK089(hu)001:9723: / de ni ngo bos phyis 'chad pa nyid las bsnyad pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:9724: de bstan pa nyid kyi phyir skyon med pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9725: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK089(hu)001:9726: zhal nas byung ba ji lta bu //
NK089(hu)001:9727: 'jig rten sgron ma nub rjes na //
NK089(hu)001:9728: gang dag mos pa tha dad pas //
NK089(hu)001:9729: lta ba'i khyad par de bzhin 'byung //
NK089(hu)001:9730: zhar las byung ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:9731: zhes pa bos nas de las mi mthun pa bstan pa gzhan yang gang ni /
NK089(hu)001:9732: zhar byung zhes par 'chad pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:9734: 'jig rten sgron ma ston pa sku mya ngan las 'das pa'i phyin /
NK089(hu)001:9735: gang dag gang zag gi blo'i mos pa mi mthun
NK089(hu)001:9736: pa tha dad pas mang pos zhal nas gsung ba'i
NK089(hu)001:9737: bka' nyid las lta ba mu stegs dang cha mthun
NK089(hu)001:9738: pa'i bye brag mang po ji lta ba khyad par
NK089(hu)001:9740: bshad pa'i mu stegs zhar las byung ba chos dang
NK089(hu)001:9741: lta ba cha ma thun pa dag kyang 'byung lugs
NK089(hu)001:9742: rjes su mthun pa'o de bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:9743: de dag ni sgo bsdur la spang bar bya ba 'ba' zhig go //
NK089(hu)001:9744: kun shes spyod pa'ang rnam pa gnyis //
NK089(hu)001:9745: rim gyis pa dang gcig char ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:9747: phyin ci ma log pa nyid dang //
NK089(hu)001:9748: sgrub byed mngon rtogs gsum nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:9749: 'di yang khyad par rnam gnyis kyis //
NK089(hu)001:9750: gsum gsum gnyis su dam pa yis //
NK089(hu)001:9751: gsung pa khyod ci mi shes sam //
NK089(hu)001:9752: des na che chung gnyis gsum drug /ces pa yang
NK089(hu)001:9753: dag pa'i lam 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa
NK089(hu)001:9754: la kun shes spyod pa'ang gnyis te /
NK089(hu)001:9755: blo dman pa'i dbang du rim gyis pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9756: blo mchog gi dpon du gcig char ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:9757: de la rim gyis 'jug pa rgyu'i theg pa ba
NK089(hu)001:9758: dper rgya gar gyi 'phong slob pa'i tshul lta bus
NK089(hu)001:9759: slob cing 'jug pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK089(hu)001:9760: don ji lta ba phyin ci ma logs pa nyid dang ma nor bar bsgrub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9761: de'i rjes su spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9762: lta bas rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9763: de yang rgyu'i theg pa chung ngu rim 'jug pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9764: dbu ma'i theg pa rim 'jug pa'i khyad par gyis bsgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK089(hu)001:9766: lta ba rtogs pa'i tshad kyang rang gzhung gsum gsum du gsungs pa yang /
NK089(hu)001:9767: theg pa chen po dang chung ngu rnams rnam grangs chung ngu gsum dang /
NK089(hu)001:9768: chen po gsum ste drug tu gsungs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9769: de la theg pa che chung gi rim 'jug gi don gsum gang snyam pa la /
NK089(hu)001:9770: bsgrub pa zab pa phra ba gnyis //
NK089(hu)001:9771: blo che zab pa dam pa nyid //
NK089(hu)001:9772: ces pa dgongs pa bsgrub pa'i thabs kyang nyan thos dang /
NK089(hu)001:9773: rang rgyal ba shes pa skad cig ma shin tu zab pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9774: phyi snod rdul phra rab shin tu cha phra ba tsam yod par rtogs nas bsgrub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9775: shes rab mchog blo che mdo sde bas chos rnams
NK089(hu)001:9776: kyi de bzhin nyid ma skyes pa'i don gting zab
NK089(hu)001:9777: la shes bya'i mchog dam pa nyid tu gyur ba
NK089(hu)001:9778: la bsgom pa'o // spyod pa rlabs chen cha shas can //
NK089(hu)001:9779: rgya che ba dang mtshan mar spyod //
NK089(hu)001:9780: zhes pa byang chub sems dpa' chub spyod pa mig dang mgo sbyin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9781: phyogs dang pha rol phyin pa rlabs chen dang /
NK089(hu)001:9783: nyan thos rang rgyal cha shas tsam mtshan mar spyod pa la brtan pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9784: de ni gsang chen gsang bar bshad //
NK089(hu)001:9785: ces pas bshad pa kho rang gi gsang ba'i don to //
NK089(hu)001:9786: mngon rtogs rnam gnyis phyi nang 'jug /mi mthun phyogs kyis gal bzung nas //
NK089(hu)001:9788: zhes pa rim 'jug gi lta ba ni blo'i bye
NK089(hu)001:9789: brag gis phyi rol theg pa chung ngu ba dang
NK089(hu)001:9790: / nang theg pa chen po dbu ma pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:9791: lta ba gzhi gcig la theg pa che chung gi
NK089(hu)001:9792: gzhung mi mthun pa'i 'dod pa 'byung rtsod pa byed
NK089(hu)001:9793: pa'o // de la theg pa chung ngu na phyi rol pa'i lta ba gang snyam pa la /
NK089(hu)001:9794: phyi rol bye brag tha snyad gnyis //
NK089(hu)001:9795: cha gnyis gcig las rtsod pa 'byung //
NK089(hu)001:9796: zhes pa phyi rol nyan thos mdo sde pa dang bye brag pa gnyis /
NK089(hu)001:9797: lta ba grub pa'i mtha' cha gnyis gzhi gcig las mi mthun par rtsod par byed pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9799: phyi nang s+n+rel zhir phyogs 'dzin cing //
NK089(hu)001:9800: gang der nges par rtsod pa 'byung //
NK089(hu)001:9801: zhes pa phyi nang gi spyod yul dag ma dag gis kyang phye ba ste /
NK089(hu)001:9802: 'dir theg pa chen po la'ang gnyis te /
NK089(hu)001:9803: rnam rig spyi yis dper na tho yor mi dang
NK089(hu)001:9804: skra'i 'khor lo mig 'khrul pa la sems snang ba
NK089(hu)001:9805: ltar / yul shes pa 'khrul pa nyid snang bar 'dod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9806: theg pa chen po mtha' bzhi dang dbus su phye nas mi dmigs par 'dod pa gnyis so //
NK089(hu)001:9807: de la sems tsam pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:9808: phyi nang s+n+rel zhir shes pa snang ba'i phyogs su
NK089(hu)001:9809: 'dod pas yul gyi phyogs gtan med par 'byung ngo
NK089(hu)001:9810: // dbu ma ni phyi'i yul dang nang gi sems
NK089(hu)001:9811: phan tshun snang ba shes pa snang bar mi 'dod
NK089(hu)001:9812: // de / kun rdzob tu sgyu ma tsam slu
NK089(hu)001:9813: bar mi bden pa yod pa 'khrul pa bden par
NK089(hu)001:9814: // de / snang yang / don dam par mtha'
NK089(hu)001:9815: bsal nas gtan la phebs pas ma skyes par 'dod
NK089(hu)001:9816: // de / snang yang / de / rang rang
NK089(hu)001:9817: gi lta ba'i phyogs 'dzin cing rtsod pa 'byung ba'i
NK089(hu)001:9819: dbus mtha' 'byed dang nges par 'jug /gtan la phebs
NK089(hu)001:9821: zhes pa dbu ma chen po mtha' dbus skyon dag pa'i blo mthong ba la blo 'jug pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9822: de'i don ma nor bar lung rigs pas gtan la phebs pas nor du rung bar byas te /
NK089(hu)001:9823: gnod pa rnams bsal nas de bzhin 'byung nges par byed pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9824: de dag 'dir yi ge'i sgras 'jigs pas rgyas par ma bkod do //
NK089(hu)001:9826: bya dang bya thabs bya med pa //
NK089(hu)001:9827: skyes dang ma skyes skye 'gag med //
NK089(hu)001:9829: ma 'dres mkha' la gza' skar bkram //
NK089(hu)001:9830: yongs su rdzogs pas mkha' khyab bdal //
NK089(hu)001:9832: ces pa gsang sngags ni gcig car 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor chen po ste /
NK089(hu)001:9833: de'i tshul ni bya ba gtsor byed kri ya dang /
NK089(hu)001:9834: gong 'og gi thabs gnyis ka la brten pa'i u pa ya dang /
NK089(hu)001:9835: ting nge 'dzin gtsor gyur pas lus ngag gi bya ba dang du mi len pa'i yo ga dang /
NK089(hu)001:9836: ting nge 'dzin gsum sogs rim pas lhar bskyed pa'i ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK089(hu)001:9837: rim pas mi bskyed pa'i a nu yo ga dang /
NK089(hu)001:9838: de dag gi tha snyad las grol ba'i a ti yo ga ste /
NK089(hu)001:9839: gsang sngags kyi theg pa drug po kun so so'i gzhung ma 'dres par gsal bzhin du /
NK089(hu)001:9840: mnyam pa chen po lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la
NK089(hu)001:9841: rdzogs pas so so'i ngo bo bstan du'ang med do
NK089(hu)001:9842: // 'o na med pa 'ba' zhig go zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:9843: so sor gsal ba'i dpe nam mkha' la gza' skar shar ba dang 'dra ste /
NK089(hu)001:9844: ma 'dres la gcig tu rdzogs pas /
NK089(hu)001:9845: kun la ma bsgos par grub pas tha snyad gnyis ka las grol ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:9846: dpe nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon shar ba dang 'dra ste /
NK089(hu)001:9847: de ltar gang zhig rig pa ni gcig char zhugs
NK089(hu)001:9848: pa med pa zhugs pa ste so so nas bgrod
NK089(hu)001:9849: pa med do // gsang sngags 'di nyid du thob bya dang lam thabs kyis btsal ba'ang med de /
NK089(hu)001:9850: chos so cog la skyes ma skyes dang skye 'gag
NK089(hu)001:9851: med par brjod pa ril rang gi mtshan nyid med
NK089(hu)001:9852: par rang byung ye shes sems nyid du bsdus pa
NK089(hu)001:9853: med par rdzogs pa'i dpe ji lta ba bzhin pa'o
NK089(hu)001:9854: // 'o na mdo sngags gnyis ka la 'jug lugs
NK089(hu)001:9855: gnyis gnyis yod bzhin 'dir rgya chad par bstan pa
NK089(hu)001:9857: rgyu yis ji ltar bgrod kyang mthar gsang sngags la rag lus dgos la /
NK089(hu)001:9858: thabs chen theg pa ni gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i phyir ro //
NK089(hu)001:9859: rmongs rim gcig car 'jug spyod pa //
NK089(hu)001:9860: zhes pa de ltar gnyis su med pa'i don gsang
NK089(hu)001:9861: ba la mdongs pa'i rgyu pa rnams rim gyis 'jug
NK089(hu)001:9862: pa dang / gsang sngags yang dag pa'i don chen po gcig char 'jug pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:9863: gnyis ka'i sems sbyongs lugs dang /
NK089(hu)001:9864: nyon mongs pa dag pa'i tshul gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:9865: 'dod pa'i yul la zhen spong dang //
NK089(hu)001:9866: sbyong sgyur shes rtog spyod dbang byed //
NK089(hu)001:9868: spyod pa blo ldan dbang bsgyur thabs //
NK089(hu)001:9869: zhes pa 'jig rten pas 'jol nyog tu spyod pa'i
NK089(hu)001:9870: chos 'di dag ni 'dod yon lnga la sogs te
NK089(hu)001:9871: / de dag 'phags pa nyan thos rang rgyal bas
NK089(hu)001:9872: ni spong zhing bkag nas dag par byed pa dang
NK089(hu)001:9873: / / byang chub sems dpas mi dmigs pa'i shes
NK089(hu)001:9874: rab dang spyod pa rgya mtshos sbyong bar byed pa
NK089(hu)001:9875: / / dang / rig sngags kri ya pa dang
NK089(hu)001:9876: u pa yas dug gsum sku gsung thugs su bsgyur
NK089(hu)001:9877: ba la sogs pa byed pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9878: rnal 'byor yo ga bas de'i mtshan nyid ji lta
NK089(hu)001:9879: ba rtogs nas lha la mchod pa tsam byed cing
NK089(hu)001:9880: spyod pa dang / rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa
NK089(hu)001:9881: yo ga pas sems snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK089(hu)001:9882: rtogs nas ched du spyod de nyon mongs pa nyid
NK089(hu)001:9883: kyis nyon mongs dbang du byed pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9884: rjes su 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor a nu yo ga
NK089(hu)001:9885: bas ji lta ba'i mtshan nyid shes shing rtogs pas
NK089(hu)001:9886: chog ste 'a gegs kyang mi 'gegs dang du ma
NK089(hu)001:9887: blangs kyang mnyam par mi lta ste btang snyoms su
NK089(hu)001:9888: byed pa dang / rnal 'byor mchog a ti yo
NK089(hu)001:9889: ga ba ni 'di nyid spu ma barjesa mdog ma
NK089(hu)001:9890: bsgyur bzo ma byas par ye nas tha snyad thams
NK089(hu)001:9891: cad ma spangs bral bar rtogs pa nyid la bya
NK089(hu)001:9892: ba ci'ang med de yal bar 'dug pa'ang med pa
NK089(hu)001:9893: nyid kyis chog pa rnams so //
NK089(hu)001:9894: shes rab 'jig rten ma rig pa las khyad par
NK089(hu)001:9895: du gyur pa'i thabs de lta bu'i don chen pos
NK089(hu)001:9896: 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i lta ba mchog dang ldan
NK089(hu)001:9897: pas gdul bya'i don bya ba'i thabs kyang ji ltar
NK089(hu)001:9898: zhe na / gang 'dir snod kyang bzhir gzigs te //
NK089(hu)001:9899: zhen chags log sred rigs rgyud can //
NK089(hu)001:9900: blo gros can gyi snod rnams la //
NK089(hu)001:9901: bstan pa rnams pa bzhi gsungs pa //
NK089(hu)001:9902: 'dod rkyen bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshigs //
NK089(hu)001:9903: ldem dgongs don dam nges pa'i tshig /snod kyi rkyen dang sbyor ba yin //
NK089(hu)001:9904: zhes pa bstan pa'i snod ni bsdu na rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK089(hu)001:9905: zhen chags can gyi gdul bya la /
NK089(hu)001:9906: 'dod pa rang rkyen gyi bstan pa rnal 'byor ma h+aa yo ga lta bu bka' stsal pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9907: log sred can gyi gdul bya la /
NK089(hu)001:9908: bkri drang brgyud pa'i bstan pa rgyu'i theg pa gsungs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9909: rigs rgyud can gyi gdul bya la /
NK089(hu)001:9910: ldem dgongs bka'i tshig kri yog gi theg pa gsungs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9911: blo gros mchog dang ldan pa'i gdul bya la /
NK089(hu)001:9912: don dam nges pa a ti yo ga gsungs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9914: snod kyi rkyen 'dod chags la sbyor ba lta bu la sogs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9915: log sred can gyi lta ba la brgyud pa'i lta ba cha 'drar bstan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9916: spyod pas rigs rgyud can la spyod pa'i ldem dgongs su bstan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9917: blo gros can la don ma nor ba sgra ji bzhin du gab sbas med par bstan pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9918: de bas na bstan pa de dag theg pa chen po nyid la tshangs kyang /
NK089(hu)001:9919: 'dir sgo bsdus pa'i dbang du theg pa kun la sbyar ro //
NK089(hu)001:9920: 'di kun shes bya'i gzhi gcig la //
NK089(hu)001:9921: 'dod pas mthong ba tha dad pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9922: zhes pa 'di kun shes bya gtan nas lta gzhi tha dad pa ma yin yang /
NK089(hu)001:9923: rang gi lta ba'i 'dod gzhung mi mthun mthong ba tha dad pa'o pas sgo so sor gyur pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9924: 'di ltar mthong sgo tha dad bzhin //
NK089(hu)001:9925: rnam par snang 'byung bkod pa la //
NK089(hu)001:9926: gang gis kun la zhugs bltas nas //
NK089(hu)001:9928: zhes pa tshul 'di bzhin lta bas mthong sgo rtogs
NK089(hu)001:9929: nas ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams su len pa'i thabs
NK089(hu)001:9930: mi mthun pa tha dad ji snyed par snang ba
NK089(hu)001:9931: ltar / theg pa'i sgo rnam par snang gyur ma
NK089(hu)001:9932: 'dres pa mang por gral bkod pa'i sgo kun nas
NK089(hu)001:9933: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis zhugs te lta ba'i
NK089(hu)001:9934: mtha' brtags nas g.yang sa dang don ngo shes par
NK089(hu)001:9935: ltar / byas te / mthar yang dag pa'i don
NK089(hu)001:9936: ma nor du 'bebs dam pa'o rung bar byas nas
NK089(hu)001:9938: ji ltar bung ba khung tshol ba //
NK089(hu)001:9939: zhes pa la sogs pa sgo kun nas bsdur ba'i dpe don dang /
NK089(hu)001:9940: dgos ched de sgra bzhin du 'grel to //
NK089(hu)001:9941: lang ka'i bdag po de dag ni /
NK089(hu)001:9942: zhes pa la sogs pa bos nas bshad pa'i don rnams ni /
NK089(hu)001:9943: 'chad pa'i phul du mkhas pas dbyung bar bslab pa'i 'byung ba'i rgyu yin te /
NK089(hu)001:9944: don gyi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9945: de skad ces smras pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9946: zhes pa dag bka' stsal pas 'khor gyis sgo kun rtogs par 'gyur ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:9947: chos thams cad kyi sgo rnam par 'byed pa 'i
NK089(hu)001:9948: le'u zhes bya ste drug cu rtsa brgyad pa bkrol
NK089(hu)001:9949: ba'o ////de nas gsang ba'i bdag pos dman pa'i lus
NK089(hu)001:9950: kyi sems dpa' rnams la smras pa /
NK089(hu)001:9951: zhes pa skyes bu 'khor la bslab pa bzhi pa gsungs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9953: kye grogs po dag mthar phyin par bya ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:9954: zhes pa la sogs pa bos nas bslab pa mthar
NK089(hu)001:9955: phyin cing phul du mkhas pas dbyung ba bslab pa
NK089(hu)001:9956: ste de nye bar ston pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:9957: theg pa chen po bsgrub pa'i thabs mang ba bsam
NK089(hu)001:9958: gyis mi khyab ji snyed pa'i rnam pa ril don
NK089(hu)001:9959: chos nyid bya bsam du med par dang bral bar
NK089(hu)001:9961: de'i bsam du med pa don gyi ngo bo ni
NK089(hu)001:9962: chos rnams kyi ji bzhin sems kyi de kho na
NK089(hu)001:9963: nyid rang rig pa 'od gsal bar mthar phyin nges
NK089(hu)001:9964: par bzung ba'o // sems kyi ngo bo de kho
NK089(hu)001:9965: na nyid ni rgyal ba thams cad kyi'ang dgongs pa'i
NK089(hu)001:9966: zhe phug dam pa 'dus pa'i de kho na nyid
NK089(hu)001:9967: par bzung ba'o // ste / de rtogs phyin chad skyed du bya ba mthar phyin gzhan med pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9968: de dag gtan tshigs kyis yid ches par bya ba'i phyir de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:9969: dgongs pa dam pa 'dus pa'i de kho na nyid
NK089(hu)001:9970: la mkhas na sems kyi de kho na nyid la
NK089(hu)001:9972: zhes pa la sogs pa dgongs pa dam pa chos
NK089(hu)001:9973: rnams kyi de kho na nyid phyin ci ma log
NK089(hu)001:9975: shes pa'i yul yin pas sems kyi de kho na nyid rang rig pa'i don go ba kho na'o //
NK089(hu)001:9976: sems kyi rtsa ba chod de gdeng du chud pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:9977: spyod yul dang bral ba'i bsam du med theg pa chen po'i don rtogs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9978: de ltar mkhas na gyur pa ni ji snyed pa'i chos rnams bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rtogs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:9979: de ltar chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid rtogs pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:9980: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas nyid de /
NK089(hu)001:9981: rgyal ba la dgongs pa de las lhag pa mi mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK089(hu)001:9982: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi dgongs pa dgongs pa
NK089(hu)001:9983: kun nas 'dus rgyud 'di nyid kyi don du mjal
NK089(hu)001:9985: de nyid rtogs par bya ba'i thabs gang snyam pa la /
NK089(hu)001:9986: grogs po dag /de bas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam pa gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:9987: 'di ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thams cad
NK089(hu)001:9988: kyi rnam pa ni rnal 'byor rnam pa gsum gyis
NK089(hu)001:9989: yongs su 'grel pa ste gsum gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:9991: bya ba byed pa 'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:9992: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK089(hu)001:9993: zhes pa bos nas bsam gyis mi khyab pa chos
NK089(hu)001:9994: thams cad rtogs par bya na rnal 'byor gsum du
NK089(hu)001:9995: phye bas brda mjal zhing go bar gyur ba ni
NK089(hu)001:9996: / shes par bya ba'i rgyu'i ngo bo rang bzhin rnal 'byor ye gnyis su med pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:9997: shes par byed pa'i rkyen lam pas don la 'bebs pa rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:9998: shes shing grub zin pa bya ba med 'bras bu
NK089(hu)001:9999: gnyis su med gyur zin pa'i rnal 'byor phyir ro
NK089(hu)001:10000: // de so so nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10001: grogs po dag bya ba'i rnal 'byor yang gsu ma du shes par bya ste /
NK089(hu)001:10003: zhes pa rnal 'byor dang po la gsum sgra bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:10004: grogs po dag de la phyi'i rnal 'byor gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10006: sa rdo rje zhes bya ba'i rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK089(hu)001:10007: de bzhin du chu rdo rje zhes bya ba la
NK089(hu)001:10008: sogs pa gsum las phyi bkar nas bstan pa ni
NK089(hu)001:10009: / 'jig rten na gang sra ba dang 'degs pa'i mtshan nyid dang las gnyis dang ldan dang /
NK089(hu)001:10013: gsal zhing go 'byed pa ni 'byung ba lnga'o //
NK089(hu)001:10014: 'dir de dag gi ngo bo nyid sems kyi dkyil
NK089(hu)001:10015: 'khor 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo nyid ye yin pa
NK089(hu)001:10016: ni / ched du ma btsal ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10017: rgyu rkyen las ma byas pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10018: mtshan nyid mi phyed pa'i phyir rdo rjer brjod pas rnal 'byor gyi ming 'thob pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10019: de bzhin du gzugs nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK089(hu)001:10023: reg nyi shu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK089(hu)001:10024: chos brgyad kyang rjes su mthun par sbyar te /
NK089(hu)001:10025: de dag sems kyi de kho na nyid du mthar
NK089(hu)001:10026: thug pa nyid mjal ba'i lta ba ni mchog go
NK089(hu)001:10027: // grogs po dag nang gi rnal 'byor ni 'di lta ste /
NK089(hu)001:10028: sems rdo rje zhes bya ba'i rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK089(hu)001:10029: zhes pa la sogs pa bos nas nang gi rnal 'byor bstan pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10030: 'gro ba rnams kyi rgyud rnam par shes pa'i tshogs
NK089(hu)001:10031: brgyad nyid bshad pa ltar gtan tshigs gsum gyis rdo
NK089(hu)001:10033: tshul de ltar de la snang ba'i rtogs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10035: shes pa'i dran rtog ji snyed pa'ang rjes su mthun
NK089(hu)001:10036: te mtha' las grol ba nyid rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10037: zhe phugs su gyur pa de /
NK089(hu)001:10038: ji lta bar gdeng du chud na mkhas pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10039: grogs po dag /phyi nang gi rnal 'byor gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10041: zhes pa la sogs pa snod bcud gnyis cha las snang ba'i rnal 'byor nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10042: yul dang shes pa gnyis ka'i cha las snang ngo cog gi snod bcud thams cad dang /
NK089(hu)001:10043: tha snyad gnyis pa'i chos gcig la ltos nas gzhag pa kha dog gnyis dang /
NK089(hu)001:10044: smra bsam la sogs rigs nges pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10046: sems can nam sangs rgyas sam bzang ba dang ngan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10048: rgyu rkyen las byas ma byas dang /
NK089(hu)001:10049: rgyu rkyen nam tha tshigs su bcas dang ma bcas pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10050: kun gyi spyi mthun dang khyad par gyi grags pa
NK089(hu)001:10051: la sogs pa ril lam pas ma byas par gdod
NK089(hu)001:10052: nas sems kyi rang bzhin de kho na nyid du
NK089(hu)001:10053: rang bzhin rnam pa gsum gyi rnam pa ye 'byor
NK089(hu)001:10055: gnyis pa'i chos ma spang sa ngang gis bral ba'i
NK089(hu)001:10056: gnyis su med pa'i don ji lta ba nyid rtogs
NK089(hu)001:10057: na mkhas pa'o // khyad par gyur ba nyid yul
NK089(hu)001:10058: med par gsal la mi g.yeng bas ming nges par
NK089(hu)001:10059: na mkhas pa'o // 'grub pa'o // grogs po dag
NK089(hu)001:10060: /de dag ni zhes pa la sogs pa go sla
NK089(hu)001:10061: ste rnal 'byor dang po'i ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10062: thun mong gi lam rgyu'i theg pa klad du khas blangs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK089(hu)001:10063: bya ba byed pa'i rnal 'byor gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10072: zhes pa lam gyi rten gzhi byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10073: pha rol tu phyin pa drug la sogs pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10075: theg pa chung ngu las dus dpag pa'i sa'i khyad par dang /
NK089(hu)001:10076: mi 'gyur ba yongs su grub pa nyid dang /
NK089(hu)001:10077: stobs bcu'i rtsal zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10078: kun nas rig pa'i gnas lnga dang bco brgyad shes pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgyu nyid do /
NK089(hu)001:10079: grogs po dag de dag kyang dgongs pa dam pa
NK089(hu)001:10080: de kho na nyid mthar phyin cing phul du gyur
NK089(hu)001:10081: pa'o // zhes pa skyes bu lang ka la sogs pa bos nas /
NK089(hu)001:10082: rgyu'i chos kyi rnam grangs de dag kyang 'dir snying
NK089(hu)001:10083: po byang chub kyi ngang du ma 'dres pa mthar
NK089(hu)001:10084: phyin rdzogs pas gsang sngags mthong ba'i brgyud pa'i rgyur
NK089(hu)001:10085: ni 'gyur gyi / don phyogs tsam la 'dir gting
NK089(hu)001:10086: phyin par rgyu yis rtogs pa ni ma yin no
NK089(hu)001:10087: ni 'gyur gyi / // yang na lam la gnas
NK089(hu)001:10088: pas rang bzhin yin pa'i don la nyams su len
NK089(hu)001:10089: cing rtsol bas rnal du phebs pa'i thabs nye bar
NK089(hu)001:10090: ni 'gyur gyi / // bstan pa ni / gzhi
NK089(hu)001:10091: dam tshig gis 'dzin pas bslab pa'i rtsa bar gyur
NK089(hu)001:10092: ni 'gyur gyi / // bstan pa ni / pa
NK089(hu)001:10093: dang / rjes su mthun pa'i spyod pa rnams dang
NK089(hu)001:10094: ni 'gyur gyi / // bstan pa ni / pa
NK089(hu)001:10095: dang / / de kho na nyid ji lta bar
NK089(hu)001:10097: phrin las kyi bye brag dang /
NK089(hu)001:10098: dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo gang gis kyang bshigs par dka' ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10099: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrib pa'i phung po rnams ldang mi nus par byed pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10100: shes rab kyis ji snyed pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10101: ji lta ba gsal bar byed pa dag kyang lam
NK089(hu)001:10102: gyi yan lag lnga bcu'i yan lag gi bya ba
NK089(hu)001:10103: byed pa yin pa'i phyir don rtogs na mkhas pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10104: phul lo // grogs po dag gzhan yang 'di lta ste /
NK089(hu)001:10119: khyab pa'i rnam pa de dag kyang /
NK089(hu)001:10120: zhes pa la sogs pa 'di dag bos nas mi mthun pa nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10121: rtsa ba'i rgyud le'u dang por gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid gsum gyi don la sbyor ba'i phyir dang /
NK089(hu)001:10122: shes rab dang snying rjes 'khor ba dang mya ngan
NK089(hu)001:10123: las 'das pa la mi gnas pa'i sku gsum dang
NK089(hu)001:10124: / sna tshogs su 'phrul bskyod pa dang pa'i cho 'phrul bcu gnyis dang /
NK089(hu)001:10125: ldem dgongs brgyad kyis gdul bya'i 'du shes bsgyur ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10126: thabs bzhi'i rtsal gyis zin par bya ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10127: rgyu yi nus pa las phyis 'byung ba'i 'bras bu mngon shes drug dang /
NK089(hu)001:10128: bkod cing bdag don du 'jug pa'i khyad par gyi lam lnga dang /
NK089(hu)001:10129: 'jug pa'i sgo bden pa gnyis dang /
NK089(hu)001:10130: shes pa gcig dang phyi nang gi chos thams cad shes pa'i phyir stong pa bco brgyad dang /
NK089(hu)001:10131: rang bzhin gyi gnas pa'i phyir chos lnga dang /
NK089(hu)001:10132: kun brjod cing ngo bo nyid du gnas pa'i sku bzhi dang /
NK089(hu)001:10133: rten te gnas pa'i phyir sa bcu'i rim pa bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10135: lam lnga dang 'gro don du 'jug pa'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis dang /
NK089(hu)001:10136: ye shes bzhi'am bco brgyad dang /
NK089(hu)001:10137: khyab pa'i rnam pa mngon par rdzogs pa'i phyir byang chub chen po ro gcig ste /
NK089(hu)001:10138: de dag gi don kyang bshad pa bzhin so so'i
NK089(hu)001:10139: mtshan nyid rtogs nas ji bzhin pa'i ngang du thag
NK089(hu)001:10140: chod na mkhas pa'i phul lo //
NK089(hu)001:10141: 'o na 'dir sku gsum dang mdzad dang ye shes
NK089(hu)001:10142: la sogs kha cig ni bya ba med pa'i rnal
NK089(hu)001:10143: 'byor du mi 'gyur ram zhes par dogs pa la
NK089(hu)001:10144: / de dag ni bsgrub par bya ba'i dmigs pa'i sgo nas bzhag pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10145: la la cha mthun par rjes 'jug par bya ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10146: la la lam gyi rgyud bsnyad pa'i sgo nas smos te /
NK089(hu)001:10147: lam nyid ma yin yang cha rkyen du tshang dgos pas the tshom gyi dogs pa med do //
NK089(hu)001:10153: yi ge'i sgo'i rnam pa de dag kyang /
NK089(hu)001:10154: dgongs pa dam pa de kho na nyid du zhes
NK089(hu)001:10155: pa dag de las mi gnas pa'i rnam pa bstan
NK089(hu)001:10156: pa ni / bden pa mthong ba'i lhag mthong lta ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10157: bying rgod pa'i sems rtse gcig pa'i zhi gnas dang /
NK089(hu)001:10158: tshig las don 'byung bas don dang mi 'bral ba'i sgo gzungs dang /
NK089(hu)001:10159: yi ge las mtshon pa tshig 'byung ba'i sgo gzungs dang /
NK089(hu)001:10160: de bzhin du bskyed pa sngags dang /
NK089(hu)001:10161: gang gis gang la bris pa'i yi ge'i sgo'i gzungs /
NK089(hu)001:10162: de dag kyang phye bas cha brgyad du 'gyur la /
NK089(hu)001:10163: de dag gi don ji lta ba bshad pa bzhin mjal ba mkhas pa'i phul lo //
NK089(hu)001:10164: de dag rnal 'byor pa'i dbu ma ngor bstan pa 'jal to //
NK089(hu)001:10165: 'bras bu gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa gzhung 'dir 'dod pa nyid gang snyam pa la /
NK089(hu)001:10166: kye grogs po dag /bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10168: zhes pa la sogs pa skyes bus bos nas rnal 'byor tha ma bstan pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10169: gsang sngags gcig char 'jug pas rgyu 'bras 'byed pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10170: rtsol ba mi byed pa'i gzhung rnam grangs nye bar
NK089(hu)001:10171: ston pa'o // sa dang zhes pa bcu ste /
NK089(hu)001:10172: 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10174: gal chen sbyong ba'i sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10175: bslab pa rgyun gyis sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10176: bsod nams gter gyi sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10177: brten pas khyad du 'gro ba'i sa /
NK089(hu)001:10178: dmigs pas 'bras bu skye ba'i sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10179: gnas pas mi 'gyur ba'i sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10180: bdal ba chos nyid kyi sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10181: rdzogs pa spyi chibs kyi sa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10185: zhes pa 'di nyid kyi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu ni lam gyi rkyen yin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10186: rgyu dang 'bras bur sbyor ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10187: thabs dang shes rab tu sbyor ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10188: dbyings dang ye shes su sbyor ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10189: sems dang chos su sbyor ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10190: las dang thugs rjer sbyor ba ni lta spyod bsdu ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10191: dpe 'dun pa sems kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10192: bka' sdod las kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10194: gsang sgo lung gi rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10195: spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10196: mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10197: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10198: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10199: yongs su rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10200: lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK089(hu)001:10203: zhes pa sgrib dang chad pa'i gnas ni drug cu po'i rtog pa brgyad cu rtsa gcig gam /
NK089(hu)001:10204: dgu bcu lam dam pa phra rags kyis gcod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10205: de bzhin du bdud chen po'i ris su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10206: mu stegs kyi khams su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10207: srin po'i khams su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10208: gnod sbyin gyi khams su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10209: ru dra chen por ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10210: bgegs chen por ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10211: lha chen po'i rigs su ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10212: sho gam gyi gcan chen du ltung ba'i sgo dang /
NK089(hu)001:10213: dmyal ba chen por ltung ba'i sgo ste /
NK089(hu)001:10214: gsang ba spyad nyes pa'i skye ltung ba gnas nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10216: zhes pa rgyu nyid 'bras bur grub pa'i phyir rgyu
NK089(hu)001:10217: 'bras gnyis su med pa'i lta ba gtan la 'bebs
NK089(hu)001:10219: lta ba dang gzhi nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10221: zhes pa mos pa'i gang zag gnyis kyi dbang du
NK089(hu)001:10222: the tshom mi za bas thabs kyis nges pa'i lam
NK089(hu)001:10223: dang / shes rab kyis nges pa'i lam gnyis te /
NK089(hu)001:10224: rgyud kyi lam gyi rtsa ba bshad pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10226: zhes pa spyod pa gzhan don gyi thabs kyis ldem po dgongs pa'i phyir bzhi ste /
NK089(hu)001:10227: mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10228: mtshan nyid kyi phyir dus gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10229: gnyen po'i phyir lan grangs gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10230: bsgyur ba'i phyir don gzhan la dgongs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10231: de'i phyir dgos ched dang ngo bos brgyad du'ang 'gyur ro //
NK089(hu)001:10233: zhes pa ye shes lnga dang /
NK089(hu)001:10234: rang byung gi ye shes so //
NK089(hu)001:10236: zhes pa kun nas tshangs pa'i phyir mnyam pa chen po dang /
NK089(hu)001:10241: 'dren pa chen po'i phyir drug go //
NK089(hu)001:10243: zhes pa mnyam pa nyid du gyur pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10244: bde ba chen por grub pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:10245: yongs su rdzogs par grub pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:10246: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa ste //
NK089(hu)001:10247: 'bras bu nyid dang lta ba'i grub mtha' thun mong pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10249: zhes pa gang bsgrub pa dngos su grub pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10250: srid pa rgya mtsho dbyings su thim par grub par gyur pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10251: 'khor ba rgya mtsho bdag gir grub par gyur pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10252: bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub par gyur pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10253: dmigs pa gang yin pa de bzhin grub par gyur ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10254: cho 'phrul thogs pa med par grub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10255: don dam bcud kyis rnam shes rgyas par grub pa ste rab 'bring tha ma gsum du gyur pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10257: zhes pa legs pa dang ldan pa'i phyir 'dod pa 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10258: yongs su khyab pa'i yon tan dang /
NK089(hu)001:10259: rlabs su che ba'i yon tan dang /
NK089(hu)001:10260: rtsis las 'das pa'i yon tan zhes bya'o //
NK089(hu)001:10263: sems kyi spyod pa gsal zhing mi gtong ba'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10264: rnam dag dbyings kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10265: thams cad rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10266: snang gsal spel 'phyo ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10267: 'byung chen sprul pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10268: dbang sgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10269: mi zad mdzod kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10270: mngon par rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10271: tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10272: rtse gcig 'phro ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10273: rin chen myu gu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10274: dug 'joms sman gyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10275: bya ba byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin te de yang spyi dang bye brag las /
NK089(hu)001:10276: bye brag la sa bcu pa la gsum /
NK089(hu)001:10277: dgu pa man chad go rims su sbyar ro //
NK089(hu)001:10278: spyir mtshan ma'i bsgrub pa tha dad dang /
NK089(hu)001:10279: ji bzhin pa'i bye brag gi sbyar ro //
NK089(hu)001:10281: zhes pa theg pa gzhan las lta bas lhag par 'phags pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10282: mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10283: bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10284: de yin pa'i sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10285: chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10286: thams cad nas thams cad sangs ma rgyas pa med pa'i che bas dpags so //
NK089(hu)001:10288: zhes pa gsal ba'i phyir stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10290: thams cad 'byung ba'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10294: cir yang mdzad pa'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10295: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10296: nam mkha' lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10297: sgyu ma lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10298: rin po che lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10299: nyi ma lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10300: snang stong gsal ba'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10301: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10302: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10303: bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes dang /
NK089(hu)001:10304: chos kyi dbyings su gsal ba'i ye shes te 'bras bu nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10306: zhes pa la gzhan don du byung zhing 'gro ba'i
NK089(hu)001:10307: tshul te mthun pa'i phyir gnas su bskyod pa dang
NK089(hu)001:10318: yang dag pa'i phyir te rgyal ba'i phrin las bshad pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10320: zhes pa yon tan gyi che ba spyom pa'i phyir
NK089(hu)001:10321: che ba nyi shu ste gnyen po med pa'i che
NK089(hu)001:10322: ba dang / 'gran zla med pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10323: khyad par 'phags pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10324: che btsan gcig pu'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10325: tsham ngam rlabs kyi che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10326: rmad du byung ba'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10327: thams cad du ma pham pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10328: mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10329: kun nas rgyal ba'i che ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10330: yongs su mi nub pa'i che ba ste don pha
NK089(hu)001:10331: rol tu phyin pa thun mong ma yin pa bcu
NK089(hu)001:10333: ye shes kyi rdo rje dang /
NK089(hu)001:10335: stobs kyi kha t+w+aam ga dang /
NK089(hu)001:10336: smon lam gyi zhing chen dang /
NK089(hu)001:10342: sbyin pa'i rin po che ste /
NK089(hu)001:10345: zhes pa le'u bcu drug pa las rol pa las
NK089(hu)001:10346: grub pa'i bdag don las phye ba ma skyes pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10347: dbu dang / ma rmongs pa'i spyan la sogs pa bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10348: gzhan don du mdzad pa las phye ba spyan gyi las gdul bya gzigs par mdzad pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10349: shangs kyi las sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad pa la sogs pa bcur bstan pa nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10351: zhes pa yang de nyid las /
NK089(hu)001:10352: sku'i rngom spyod bye ba sa yar mngon pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10353: gsung gi rngom spyod bstan pa rgya mtshor mngon pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10354: thugs kyi rngom spyod chos nyid nam mkhar mngon pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10355: mthu'i rngam spyod nam mkha'i dbyings ltar mngon pa bzhi las /
NK089(hu)001:10356: yan lag bzhi bzhi ste tshul bcu drug dang nyi shu'o //
NK089(hu)001:10358: zhes pa yang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga la /
NK089(hu)001:10359: brjid bzhi bzhi ste nyi shu gsungs pa de nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10363: chu'i phung po rngub ste skam pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10364: rlung gi bskal pa bcings pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10365: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'bum dgye ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10366: sreg pa'i bskal pa chen po gsum gzhil ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10367: nam mkha' thams cad ba spu gcig gis gang bar byas pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10368: ba spu gcig las sangs rgyas bye ba dgye ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10369: sangs rgyas bye ba ba spu gcig gi nang du shong bar bya ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10370: 'khor ba thams cad ba spu gcig gis nang du rngub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10371: ba spu gcig gis 'khor ba thams cad khyab par bya ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10372: bskal pa'i 'khor lo ring du bsring ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10374: dus kyi 'khor lo mnyam par sbyar ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10376: las kyi 'khor lo chen po rgyun gcod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10377: las rgyun du bskor ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10378: srid pa'i 'khor lo bzlog pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10380: sdug bsngal gyi 'khor lo chen po rgyun gcad pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10381: dmyal ba'i 'khor lo chen po dong sprug pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10383: zhes pa'ang nyi shu ste le'u de nyid las /
NK089(hu)001:10384: las kyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK089(hu)001:10385: bsam gtan gyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK089(hu)001:10387: thugs rje bzhi la yan lag bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug dang nyi shu'o //
NK089(hu)001:10388: yongs su rdzogs pa'i rnam par dag pa dgongs pa
NK089(hu)001:10389: dam pa de kho na nyid du mthar phyin cing
NK089(hu)001:10391: zhes pa rnam grangs thams ca da byang chub kyi
NK089(hu)001:10392: sems bde ba chen por rdzogs par grub pa'i phyir
NK089(hu)001:10393: gcig ste bzhi nyid kho na'o //
NK089(hu)001:10394: de bas na 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor 'di ni gzhi
NK089(hu)001:10395: nyid dang lam dang 'bras bur bsdus te 'grel ba'o
NK089(hu)001:10396: // de lta bu bya ba med pa gsang sngags kyi rnam grangs de dag ni /
NK089(hu)001:10397: de kho na nyid du gnas zin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10398: de nyid du bya ba med pas 'byin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10399: des phyin pa'i phyir mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10400: 'di dag ji lta bar ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pa ni mkhas pa'i phul lo //
NK089(hu)001:10401: 'o na 'dir yang bya ba med pa'i lam rnams
NK089(hu)001:10402: smros pa bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor du mi
NK089(hu)001:10404: 'dir de dag gtso bo'i dbang du bya ba med
NK089(hu)001:10405: pa'i yon tan de dag tu snang bas ril 'bras
NK089(hu)001:10406: bu la rdzogs pas smros pa mi 'gal ba dang
NK089(hu)001:10407: / 'bras bu grub par byed pa'i rgyu rkyen 'dir
NK089(hu)001:10408: 'brel ba'i sgo nas smros kyang gtso bor 'bras bu
NK089(hu)001:10409: nyid du bstan pa'i phyir 'gal ba med do //
NK089(hu)001:10410: mdor rkyen gyi rnal 'byor la 'bras bu smros pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10411: 'bras bu rnal 'byor la lam smros pa gnyis ka'ang /
NK089(hu)001:10412: gtso bor gang ston pa dbang du gyur bas mi mthun pas smros pa bzhin du 'gyur ro //
NK089(hu)001:10413: chos 'di dag gi rnam grangs la dpag nas le'u
NK089(hu)001:10414: mtshams rnal 'byor gsum bsdu ba bshad pa'ang shin tu
NK089(hu)001:10415: gsal lo // phul du byung ba'i mdor dpe don gyis gces par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10416: de yang ji ltar zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10418: ji ltar mthon ri rtse dag la //
NK089(hu)001:10419: zhes pa la sogs pa phul du mkhas pas dbyung
NK089(hu)001:10420: ba'i dpe don ste sgra ji bzhin du sbyar ba
NK089(hu)001:10421: ni go sla'o // de skad ces smras pas /
NK089(hu)001:10422: zhes pa dag 'khor gyis mkhas pa'i don zab mo thob pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10423: le'u'i mtshan te bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10424: le'u ste drug cu dgu pa 'grel pa'o ////thabs kyi
NK089(hu)001:10425: nges pa'i lam dam pa shes rab kyi sngon du
NK089(hu)001:10427: de nas yang gsang ba'i bdag pos dman pa dam pa rnams la smras pa /
NK089(hu)001:10428: kye grogs po dag thams cad du 'du bar bya ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:10433: zhes pa bslab pa bzhi pa bstan ma thag par /
NK089(hu)001:10434: skyes bus bslab pa lnga pa 'khor la gsungs pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10435: rim pa dbang gis bsgrod pa'i bslab pa nye bar bstan pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:10437: de la gsum du phye ba ni sgra bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:10438: de dag so so nas gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10439: grogs po dag de la bya ba ni bsdu ba'i bya bas so //
NK089(hu)001:10440: zhes pa bos nas dang po bkar nas ston pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10441: yon tan thob bya dbang thob par bya ba'i phyir dang po nod pa'i las rtsom pa nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10442: rang bzhin ni chos nyid kyis so //
NK089(hu)001:10443: zhes pa dbang gi rang bzhin ni ye nas rang
NK089(hu)001:10444: gi sems rang bzhin dang chos nyid la rten 'brel
NK089(hu)001:10445: gyi mthu ma btsal bar gnas pa nyid do //
NK089(hu)001:10446: bsgyur bas 'dul bar bya ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:10451: zhes pa dag dbang bskur ba 'i thabs rkyen gyis
NK089(hu)001:10452: slong ba'i don nye bar bstan pa ni rnam grangs
NK089(hu)001:10454: grogs po dag de la rgyu ni yo byad chen po lnga kho na'o //
NK089(hu)001:10455: zhes pa skyes bus bos nas grangs la snyegs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10456: rgyu bkar nas ston pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10457: bskur ba'i rgyu dang thob par bya ba'i rgyu gnyis las /
NK089(hu)001:10458: 'dir thun mong ma yin pa'i yo byad chen po lngas phyug pa'i bla ma'i byin dang /
NK089(hu)001:10459: slob bu lnga dang ldan pa'i snod gnyis ka thun mong du mjal bar bya'o //
NK089(hu)001:10464: zhes pa la sogs pa dbang bskur ba'i dus ni /
NK089(hu)001:10465: rnal 'byor pa gcig gi rgyud la zag bcas kyi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu rdzogs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10466: lha'i sku la mtshan bcas mtshan med blo goms pa'i dus dang /
NK089(hu)001:10467: mkhas pa nyams can dam can 'du ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10468: gsang sngags lta ba gsal ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10469: sems kyi ting nge 'dzin bdag don du bsgom mi dgos pa las su rung ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10470: ting nge mthar phyin pa'i drod rtags 'byung ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10471: nges ma nges kyi skye bo mang pos basngagasa pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10472: sgra bzhin min par rig pa gdeng dang ldan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10473: bdag gzhan gyi bya ba rdzogs te las gang la'ang
NK089(hu)001:10474: thogs pa med par shes pa'i yon tan dgu dang
NK089(hu)001:10475: ldan na dus su phyin pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10476: 'o na 'di dag 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor la ldan nam zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10477: 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor la ril mi ldan pas dbang yang rdzogs par ma bskur te /
NK089(hu)001:10478: sngon du bya ba'i las su gyur pas nyan pa'i dbang glegs bam gyi bskur ba tsam mo //
NK089(hu)001:10479: 'di dag ni dbang rdzogs par bskur ba'i dus su bstan pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:10480: sa pa la mang nyung du ldan pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10481: grogs po dag tshad ni 'di lta ste /
NK089(hu)001:10482: zhes pa dbang thob pa'i tshad nye bar bstan pa'i rnam grangs so //
NK089(hu)001:10483: grogs po dag ded dpon gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10490: zhes pa bos nas thob pas bdag gzhan gyis 'dren
NK089(hu)001:10491: dpon dam pa bla ma nyid du gyur pa ni
NK089(hu)001:10492: / shes bya thams cad de las byas chog la goms pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10493: gsang ba'i don ji ltar rtogs pa'i gdeng dang ldan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10494: man ngag lhan cig 'grogs bde bas phyag rgya mo rang dbang med par 'du ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10495: bla ma'i man ngag dbang brgyud ma chad pa gab tshul bstan pa thob pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10496: dbang gi don bslab pa dang bsnyen bsgrub dbang dang man ngag mthar thug pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:10498: grogs po dag snga ltas ni 'di lta ste /
NK089(hu)001:10503: zhes pa dbang thob pa'i snga ltas ni bzhi ste /
NK089(hu)001:10504: lta ba don ma nor ba mthong ba'i ltas thob pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10505: don la gom pas 'byor pa'i ltas thob cing ngo mtshar can gyi rdzas rnyed pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10506: 'dod pa grub gzhan la rag ma lus pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10507: 'gro ba la phan thogs pa'i nus pa thob pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10508: lung bstan pa lo rgyus sbyar te /
NK089(hu)001:10509: mdor na dur khrod khu byug rol pa'i mdo las gsungs pa ji bzhin no //
NK089(hu)001:10510: grogs po dag smin pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK089(hu)001:10511: mngon spyod dang mi skyor ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:10512: zhes pa dag thob pa'i tshad 'bras bur gyur pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:10513: dbang gang la thob pa'i chos de lta ba'i nyams
NK089(hu)001:10514: skyes byin rlabs che thugs rje 'byung bdag gzhan do
NK089(hu)001:10515: na du spyod pa dngos su byed pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10516: nyan dbang thob nas nyan pa la sogs pa lta bu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10517: thob pas dbang gang gi nus pa rdzogs phyir gang
NK089(hu)001:10518: la'ang nyams mi nga bas yang zlos mi dgos pa'o
NK089(hu)001:10519: // grogs po dag grags pa gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10521: gang chu bo bzhi'i rgyud du byung ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10526: zhes pa bos nas grags pa lnga thob pa ste /
NK089(hu)001:10527: dbang thob nas grags pa ni bshad pa'i chu bo
NK089(hu)001:10528: bzhi sngon 'byung gi rgyud 'dzin par byung ba dang
NK089(hu)001:10529: / 'jig rten pa'i lam theg pa gzhan la thob
NK089(hu)001:10530: pa las gzhan dag las dbang thob pas khyad par
NK089(hu)001:10531: / gyur pa dang / dbang gi don ji lta
NK089(hu)001:10532: ba nyid bla ma'i tshad mi 'bral bar yod pa
NK089(hu)001:10533: / gyur pa dang / dang / rgyud dang mdzod gsum phrin las dang /
NK089(hu)001:10534: 'gro ba 'dul pa'i thabs dbang phrin las ril la mkhas shing goms pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10535: ma thob pa ma yin dbang du bya ba rigs kyi chu bo /
NK089(hu)001:10537: man ngag /nyams kyi chu bo bzhi'o ril thob pa nyid de /
NK089(hu)001:10538: de dag ni re re nas rnal 'byor lnga'i rim par yang 'gal ba med do //
NK089(hu)001:10539: de dag gang gang la ji ltar grags pa ltar sbyar ro //
NK089(hu)001:10540: grogs po dag gegs gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10545: zhes pa bos nas dbang thob tu mi ster ba'i
NK089(hu)001:10546: gegs sgrib pa chu bo'i rnyogs ma lta bu ni
NK089(hu)001:10547: / bsdu na rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK089(hu)001:10549: ma bskur ba mi ldan pa dus la ma babs pa dad pa dang gus pa med pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10550: snod med bcud bral kun stong pa //
NK089(hu)001:10551: de ni dbang thob ma yin no //
NK089(hu)001:10553: gsang med brjed ngas dbang mi chags //
NK089(hu)001:10554: dam med g.yeng rmugs dbang mi 'gos //
NK089(hu)001:10555: dad med blo zhen rdzob pa che //
NK089(hu)001:10556: dam nyams skur pa can dad pa log cing gsang ba 'chol /
NK089(hu)001:10557: tshul 'chos mkhan la ras chod byed //
NK089(hu)001:10566: zhes pa tshul bzhin thob pa'i rtags ni bzhi ste /
NK089(hu)001:10567: thams cad du yo na tan grags pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10568: snga ma'i spyod yul las gyen du 'byung ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10569: byin brlabs dang man ngag dang rten 'brel gyi 'khor
NK089(hu)001:10570: ba rgyun chad nus pa stobs can du gyur pas
NK089(hu)001:10571: gzhan gyis mi tshugs shing rang gzhung brtan pa dang
NK089(hu)001:10572: / bsgrubs na las dang dngos grub thams cad mngon du shar zhing yon tan snang ba'ang rgyus dabye'o //
NK089(hu)001:10573: grogs po dag thob pa gang zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10577: zhes pa bos nas dang po thob pa'i tshul bstan pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10578: rdo rje rgyal po bla mas byin pas thob pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10579: rang rig pa'i rtsal gyis thob pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10580: 'di dag rgyud gcig dang tha dad pa gnyis ka thun mong du 'gyur ro //
NK089(hu)001:10581: de la 'byin pas thob pa'ang rtsal dang sbyar nas byin pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10582: grogs po dag de yang 'di ltar thob par rig par bya ste /
NK089(hu)001:10583: gang 'dir snying rje'i yul rnams la //
NK089(hu)001:10584: zhes pa la sogs pa bos nas thob pa'i tshul bstan pa'i phyir smos pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10585: bla ma'i dbang gi thugs rje'i yul du gyur pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10586: slob bu kun lam lnga la zhugs pa gong ma
NK089(hu)001:10587: gong ma'i bla ma'i byin kho na'o //
NK089(hu)001:10588: 'byung ba ni rtogs pa dang nus pa khyad par
NK089(hu)001:10589: can la phan pa'i byin rlabs 'byung ba'i dbang gang
NK089(hu)001:10590: yang rung ba bskur ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:10591: rim pas dang por 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor tshogs lam las dang po ba dag la /
NK089(hu)001:10592: gsung rab sde yan lag bcu gnyis kyi glegs bam
NK089(hu)001:10593: gyis nyan cing slob pa'i rten yin pas nyan pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10595: sbyor lam rigs chen 'byed pa la thabs shes rab
NK089(hu)001:10596: snang stong gnyis kyis bdag gzhan don la sbyor ba'i
NK089(hu)001:10597: phyir / nyi zla'i gzugs sbyin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10598: rnam pa gzhan du thabs shes rab kyi sems sbyin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10599: dbugs chen 'byin pa la 'khor sgyur cha byad kyi
NK089(hu)001:10600: rat+na bdun gzhan don rin po che sna bdun sbyin
NK089(hu)001:10601: pa dang / lung chen thob pa la dam pa
NK089(hu)001:10602: rnams kyis sras su byin gyis brlabs pas bkra shis
NK089(hu)001:10603: kyi rdzas brgyad sbyin pas thob pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10604: rtsal chen rdzogs pa la sid+d+hi dang mthu la sogs
NK089(hu)001:10605: pa'i rtsal rdzogs te mnyam pa la 'jog stobs bcu'i
NK089(hu)001:10606: dbang thob pa stobs bcus mi mthun pa gnon cing
NK089(hu)001:10607: stobs bcu dang / sa kun gyi yang tog de
NK089(hu)001:10608: nyid kyis rin po che stong 'bar ba'i dbang thob
NK089(hu)001:10610: de dag ni rang rang gi rtsal dang cha mthun du byin pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10612: ma thob gzu lum rang bshad pa //
NK089(hu)001:10613: zhes pa dag rgyud 'di dbang ma thob par bshad pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10614: bka' rab 'byams la bltas kyang de 'bras bu thob par mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:10616: bka' rnam gnyis bcag pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10617: gzhung dang 'gal ba'i las gnyis byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK089(hu)001:10618: ji ltar rgyal rigs rgyud byung ba //
NK089(hu)001:10619: zhes pa la sogs pa rim pa dbang gis bgrod
NK089(hu)001:10620: dgos par dpe don gnyis kyi bstan pa ste sgra
NK089(hu)001:10622: de skad ces smras pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10623: dman pa dam pa dag lung dam pa bstan pa'i drod thob par gyur to //
NK089(hu)001:10624: zhes pa skyes bus bka' stsal pas 'khor rnams rang
NK089(hu)001:10625: rang rtsal tshad kyi dbang so so bskur bas gang
NK089(hu)001:10626: 'byung ba'i lung bstan pa'i rig pa nyams rnyed par
NK089(hu)001:10627: gyur pa'o // rnal 'byoor dam pa lung bstan pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10628: le'u ste bdun cu pa bkral ba'o ////de nas yang
NK089(hu)001:10629: gsang ba'i bdag po des dman pa'i lus kyi sems
NK089(hu)001:10631: zhes pa rim pa dbang gis bgrod pa bstan ma thag par /
NK089(hu)001:10632: skyes bus 'khor la bos nas bslab pa drug pa
NK089(hu)001:10633: la spyod pas dor ba'i bslab pa nye bar bstan
NK089(hu)001:10635: gang go cha gyon pa'i rjes su mi ldog par 'gro ba ste /
NK089(hu)001:10636: zhes pa la sogs pa yid la dam bcas pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10637: lta bas chod tshad kyi rjes su spyod pa mi
NK089(hu)001:10639: de yang chos rnams kyi chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10640: rjes su 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK089(hu)001:10641: chos mang po brjod pa las 'das pa rnams 'gro
NK089(hu)001:10643: nam mkha'i rjes su chen po bzhi 'gro ba ltar /
NK089(hu)001:10644: rang rig pa'i de kho na nyid kyi rjes su
NK089(hu)001:10645: sems las byung ba'i 'du byed rnams 'gro ba dang
NK089(hu)001:10646: / chos ma bcos pa'i ngang du chos so cog
NK089(hu)001:10647: 'gro ba ni 'dir don dper blang ba kho na'o
NK089(hu)001:10648: / // de bzhin du dgongs pa dam pa'i rjes su gang gsungs pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10649: gang mdzad pa thams cad 'gro bas na /
NK089(hu)001:10650: zhes pa la sogs pa bshad pa'i dpe de ltar
NK089(hu)001:10651: rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa mnyam pa chen po'i
NK089(hu)001:10653: phrin las mdzad pa thams cad de las mi 'da'
NK089(hu)001:10654: zhing 'dus pas rgyud 'di las ji ltar bka' stsal
NK089(hu)001:10655: pa ltar rnal 'byor lam pa rnams kyi spyod pa'ang
NK089(hu)001:10656: lta ba'i rjes su mthun par spyad pa ni thabs
NK089(hu)001:10657: bstan pa'o // de dag rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10658: grogs po dag de yang 'di lta ste /
NK089(hu)001:10659: mnyam dang mi mnyam mi mnyam mnyam //
NK089(hu)001:10660: kun nas mi mnyam yongs kyis mnyam //
NK089(hu)001:10661: zhes pa bos nas lta ba'i rjes su spyad thabs rgyas par nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10662: mnyam dang blang dor med pa'i don mnga' ba'i rgyal ba rnams dang /
NK089(hu)001:10663: mi mnyam bzang ngan spang len gyi mtha' la zhen pa'i 'khor ba ni /
NK089(hu)001:10664: mi mnyam rtogs ma rtogs kyi dbang gis bde sdug khyad par shin tu che yang /
NK089(hu)001:10665: ngo bo nyid mtha' gnyis las grol mnyam pa'i don du che chung med do //
NK089(hu)001:10666: 'o na thams cad du gcig pa kho na 'am zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10667: de ltar kun nas mi mnyam pa'ang rgyu rkyen 'bras
NK089(hu)001:10668: bu ril nas so so bas mi mnyam pas yongs
NK089(hu)001:10669: zhig kyang 'khrul pa'i ngo la khyad par snang ba'o
NK089(hu)001:10670: // 'on kyang de dag gsang sngags kyi ngo bo
NK089(hu)001:10671: sems kyi dkyil 'khor yongs kyis 'od gsal bas snubs
NK089(hu)001:10672: tshabs che chung med pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10673: ma 'dres la mnyam yongs su rdzogs pa kho na ste lta ba'i mchog go //
NK089(hu)001:10674: de yi rjes su spyad pa yang //
NK089(hu)001:10675: gsang sngags spyod pa'i khyad par yang //
NK089(hu)001:10676: gang dang don gyis mnyam par spyad //
NK089(hu)001:10677: ces pa gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK089(hu)001:10678: pa'i spyod pa'ang lta ba mnyam pa chen po dang
NK089(hu)001:10679: gang dang don gyis ya char ma gyur pas blang
NK089(hu)001:10680: dor med mnyam par spyad pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10681: byin gyis rlabs kyi spyod pa'am //
NK089(hu)001:10682: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi spyod pa ste //
NK089(hu)001:10683: zhes pa la sogs pa de dag gi tshul ni /
NK089(hu)001:10684: lta bas ji ltar mjal ba'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10685: byin gyis rlabs shugs kyi spyod pa'i dpe ni nam mkha' dang 'dra'o //
NK089(hu)001:10686: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa la rtogs pas dbang bsgyur nas spyod pa ni rgyal po dang 'dra zhing /
NK089(hu)001:10687: 'gro ba'i 'dul thabs brtul zhugs chen po'i spyod pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10688: dper na me dpung chen po dang /
NK089(hu)001:10689: chu bo chen po lta bu spyad par bya'o //
NK089(hu)001:10690: de dag ni don gcig pa dpe bzhir yang 'gyur ro //
NK089(hu)001:10691: de yang de yul che chung gis //
NK089(hu)001:10692: khyad par nyid kyis brlabs pa yin //
NK089(hu)001:10693: zhes pa dag spyod pa de dag kyang dgongs pa
NK089(hu)001:10694: che chung gis spyod pa'i khyad par che chung yang
NK089(hu)001:10695: lta bas byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10696: dpe rgyal po yang sku bsod nams kyi stobs 'dul
NK089(hu)001:10697: zhing che chung gis mnga' thang gi dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK089(hu)001:10698: yul ljongs dang grong khyer dang rgyal khams che chung
NK089(hu)001:10699: yod pa ltar / theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor pa'i bdag gzhan gyi spyod pa'i khyad par yang /
NK089(hu)001:10700: rnal 'byor rnam sngags tshul pa lnga dang bcu'i spyod pa'ang khyad par skas gdangs bzhin yod do //
NK089(hu)001:10701: lnga'i spyod pa ni de ltar snang bshad pa dag go //
NK089(hu)001:10702: bcu'i spyod pa ni 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK089(hu)001:10703: de yang dpe nye bar mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10704: thabs chen spyod la 'jug pa yang //
NK089(hu)001:10705: bab tshod thad du 'jug pa ste //
NK089(hu)001:10706: dper na glang chen chur 'jug pa //
NK089(hu)001:10707: zhes pa dag sgra bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK089(hu)001:10708: ji ltar nus tshad de spyod phyir //
NK089(hu)001:10709: sa dang gnas skabs ye shes dang //
NK089(hu)001:10710: sgrib dang gol sa rtog pa dang //
NK089(hu)001:10711: spyod dang dam tshig ting 'dzin dang //
NK089(hu)001:10712: dus dang dngos grub mthar phyin dang //
NK089(hu)001:10713: lta ba'i khyad par gnas gyur rnams //
NK089(hu)001:10714: zhes pa la sogs pa rnal 'byor lta ba'i khyad
NK089(hu)001:10715: par gyis spyod pa'ang rang rang gi nus tshad dang
NK089(hu)001:10716: sbyar nas spyod pa la khyad par yod pa'i phyir
NK089(hu)001:10718: 'du shes 'gyur ba'i skabs lnga'am bcu'i khyad par dang /
NK089(hu)001:10721: gong 'og mthong ma mthong gi sgrib pa lnga bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10722: gong ma 'og mar ltung ba'i gol sa lnga dang bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10723: don lha la rtog pa lnga'am bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10724: de bzhin du spyod pa'i khyad par dang /
NK089(hu)001:10725: bsrung bya'i dam tshig ngo bo ba gang la dam pa gang ldan pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10726: thun mong du bsrung ba gang yin pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10727: ting nge 'dzin yid la byed pa yan chad lnga dang bcu'i gsal mi gsal gyi rim pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10728: sa 'og gis gong ma bsgrub pa'i dus lnga'am bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10729: spyir byang chub chen po nyid grub pa'i dus dang /
NK089(hu)001:10730: dngos grub chen po dang gnas skabs kyi lam mthar phyin pas gong ma 'grub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10731: lta ba'i rtogs tshad kyi khyad par mthar phyin pa la bcu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10732: kun gzhi lngar gnas gyur pa'i tshul gyis lan bcur yang 'gyur ba ste /
NK089(hu)001:10733: re shig pa dang gtan du bar sbyar ro //
NK089(hu)001:10734: de yang gnas ngan len gnas gyur dang /
NK089(hu)001:10736: chos nyid gnas gyur du 'grel to //
NK089(hu)001:10737: de dag thams cad gzhi gcig las med na'ang rnam grangs dang /
NK089(hu)001:10738: khyad par du dbye ba'i dgongs pa bye brag rnams ni /
NK089(hu)001:10739: gang zag lam pa'i snod kyi blo rtsal dang sbyar
NK089(hu)001:10740: nas chud mi gsan pa'i 'dul thabs su khyad pa
NK089(hu)001:10741: ra cir yang tha dad par bstan pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10742: de na khas blangs pa'i sa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10744: spyir thun mong du spyad pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10746: de la thun mong du spyad pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10747: spyod pa rgyun gyi dam tshig bzhi dang /
NK089(hu)001:10748: gso bslang gi spyod pa yan lag dang bcas pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10749: brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa nyi shu dang /
NK089(hu)001:10750: 'gro don gyi spyod pa gsum bshad pa dag go //
NK089(hu)001:10751: khyad par bdag don sgo'i spyod pa ni /
NK089(hu)001:10752: sa dang po la rnam par dkar ba tshogs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10753: sa gnyis pa la phra men gyi spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10754: sa gsum pa la brtson 'grus kyi spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10755: sa bzhi pa la g.yeng ba spang pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10756: sa lnga pa la yongs su mi gtong ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10757: sa drug pa la shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10758: bdun pa la ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10759: brgyad pa la spong len med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10760: dgu pa la ye shes thugs rje'i spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10761: sa bcu pa la bya ba med pa 'i spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10762: de dag kyang bsdu na bya ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10763: bya ba med pa gnyis su 'dus te /
NK089(hu)001:10766: gang yang bdag gi don dang /
NK089(hu)001:10768: de dag gang gis yid ches par 'gyur zhe na /
NK089(hu)001:10771: gnas shing spyad pa'i sa zhes bya //
NK089(hu)001:10772: dag dang ma dag gis spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10773: dge dang mi dge'i las rnams kun //
NK089(hu)001:10774: gnod spyod sbyor ba'i tshul nyid kyis //
NK089(hu)001:10776: ngan song mi ldog dgon par 'jug /spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor nyid //
NK089(hu)001:10777: mos pa dag cing 'dun pa'i gnas //
NK089(hu)001:10778: bden mthong cir spyod mi dmigs ldan //
NK089(hu)001:10779: khyad par rtsal 'phangs kun rdzogs shing //
NK089(hu)001:10781: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal chen po //
NK089(hu)001:10782: mthong ba'i gnas na bcu drug pa //
NK089(hu)001:10783: rdzogs pa'i gnas na longs spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10784: yul don ye shes de sbyar bas //
NK089(hu)001:10785: shes par bya ba thams cad rdzogs //
NK089(hu)001:10786: sgyu ma'ang sgyu ma yin spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10787: cir snang ci yang ma yin pas //
NK089(hu)001:10788: mi skye mi 'gag ngo bo las //
NK089(hu)001:10789: ji ltar bltas dgu der snang bas //
NK089(hu)001:10790: theg mchog spyi rgya rlabs kyis bcad //
NK089(hu)001:10792: the tshom gyi dogs pa med par mjal to //
NK089(hu)001:10793: rang rang gi spyod pa dang mi 'tshams pa'i spyod pa gol bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10794: de yang rtsal gyi khyad par gyis /
NK089(hu)001:10795: dang po las kyi rnal 'byor la //
NK089(hu)001:10796: sogs pa'i rnal 'byor chung ngu rnams //
NK089(hu)001:10797: rang rang rtsa ba bor nas ni //
NK089(hu)001:10798: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor las //
NK089(hu)001:10799: zhes pa la sogs las dang po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10801: bslab par sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10803: bka' sdod las kyi rnal 'byor pa lta spyod dman chung ngu pa kun gyis /
NK089(hu)001:10804: rang rang gis spyod pa 'tshams rtsa ba bor ba bzhag nas rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10805: rmad byung rol sogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10807: rol pa rgyan gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10808: bde ba chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10809: thig le chen por rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10810: bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10811: lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK089(hu)001:10812: klong yangs chub pa'i rnal 'byor chen po dag gi
NK089(hu)001:10813: spyod pa'i tshul du spyod par byed dang don 'dod
NK089(hu)001:10814: pas 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa ni tshi chad
NK089(hu)001:10815: de / dper na sbal bus nam mkha' la lding bar 'dod kyang /
NK089(hu)001:10816: slar btsal ba'i yul yin tshi chad de mi 'grub pa dang /
NK089(hu)001:10817: nongs bus rgyal dpe don tshig bdun thabs mi myong ba dang 'a dra ste 'brel ba med do //
NK089(hu)001:10818: 'on kyang rgyud nas mi thob pa ma yin no //
NK089(hu)001:10819: de phyir dgongs pa kun 'dus pas //
NK089(hu)001:10821: gso dang spyod pa'i spyod pa dag /dam pa dag dang mnyam par gsungs //
NK089(hu)001:10822: zhes pa de phyir bshad pa'i gtan tshigs kyis dgongs pa kun 'dus rgyud 'di la /
NK089(hu)001:10823: gang skabs 'dir las dang po'i rnal 'byor la sogs
NK089(hu)001:10824: pa'i blo dman pa'i ched du gso ba'i spyod pa
NK089(hu)001:10825: dang / sgrib pa sbyong ba'i spyod pa gnyis spyad na /
NK089(hu)001:10826: dam pa dag rgyal ba rnams kyi go 'phang mnyam
NK089(hu)001:10827: par thob par bdag gzhan gyi spyod par gsung bka'
NK089(hu)001:10828: stsal pa'o // gso dang bslang ba'i rtog pa 'di //
NK089(hu)001:10829: rtog pa can dang mthun par sbyar //
NK089(hu)001:10830: zhes pa 'chad pa'i nad gso ba dang /
NK089(hu)001:10831: lta ngan du shi ba bslang ba'i spyod rtog ni /
NK089(hu)001:10832: mu stegs dag drang ba'i phyir yang spyad de /
NK089(hu)001:10833: 'dir brda yis dngos por spyod pa'o //
NK089(hu)001:10835: gso ba rtogs pas zin pa'i nad //
NK089(hu)001:10837: gtsang dme skye shi la sogs pa'i rtog pa'i nad gso ba'o //
NK089(hu)001:10839: dgongs spyod mnyam pa chen pos gso ba'i phyir /
NK089(hu)001:10840: lta spyod mnyam pa'i sman gyis gso //
